Class Staff

Object
User
Staff
public class Staff extends User
The Staff class represents a staff member in the system, inheriting from the User class. It includes methods for creating, managing, and viewing camps, as well as handling camp-related tasks.
Author:
Gao Linyue, Tey Cia Meng
